vars: {
  d2-config: {
    layout-engine: elk
    theme-id: 6
  }
}
title: |md
  ## Thread Pool Worker Loop
  **Mutex / Condition Variable State Transitions**
  *Single worker thread lifecycle вЂ” pool->lock held в–ј / released в–І*
| {near: top-center}
classes: {
  normal_state: {
    shape: rectangle
    style: {
      border-radius: 8
      font-size: 14
      bold: true
    }
  }
  error_state: {
    shape: rectangle
    style: {
      fill: "#FF4444"
      font-color: white
      border-radius: 8
      font-size: 14
      bold: true
      stroke: "#CC0000"
      stroke-width: 3
    }
  }
  terminal_state: {
    shape: rectangle
    style: {
      fill: "#444444"
      font-color: white
      border-radius: 8
      font-size: 14
      bold: true
      stroke: "#222222"
      stroke-width: 3
    }
  }
}
initial: {
  shape: circle
  label: ""
  width: 24
  height: 24
  style: {
    fill: black
    stroke: black
  }
}
WAITING: "WAITING\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nBlocked inside\npthread_cond_wait()\nLock: RELEASED в–І\nby cond_wait\nautomatically\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nInvariant:\ncount == 0 OR\nshutdown checked\nnext wakeup" {
  class: normal_state
  style.fill: "#B5AFF6"
  style.stroke: "#7B6FD4"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
WOKEN: "WOKEN\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nReturned from\npthread_cond_wait()\nLock: HELD в–ј\nRe-evaluating\nwhile condition:\ncount==0 && !shutdown\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nHandles spurious\nwakeups via WHILE" {
  class: normal_state
  style.fill: "#E4DBFE"
  style.stroke: "#7B6FD4"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
SHUTDOWN_CHECK: "SHUTDOWN_CHECK\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nshutdown == 1\n&& count == 0\nLock: HELD в–ј\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nTermination path:\nunlock + return NULL\nAll joins released\nvia pthread_join()" {
  class: terminal_state
}
DEQUEUING: "DEQUEUING\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nLock: HELD в–ј\nOperations:\nвЂў Copy queue[head]\n  (24 bytes)\nвЂў head = (head+1)\n  % CAPACITY\nвЂў count--\nвЂў cond_signal\n  (not_full)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nO(1) critical section\n< 500 ns hold time" {
  class: normal_state
  style.fill: "#88DCF7"
  style.stroke: "#3A8FB5"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
UNLOCKED: "UNLOCKED\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nLock: RELEASED в–І\nHolds: work_item\n(local copy on stack)\nclient_fd transferred\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nPreparing to call\nhandle_client_keep_alive()\nAll N workers can\nbe here in parallel" {
  class: normal_state
  style.fill: "#C7F1FF"
  style.stroke: "#3A8FB5"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
HANDLING: "HANDLING\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nLock: RELEASED в–І\nExecuting:\nhandle_client_keep_alive\n  (client_fd, ip, port,\n   doc_root)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nMay run 0вЂ“30s\nReads from socket\nServes files\nCloses client_fd\nbefore returning\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nstats & log updated\nunder their own mutexes" {
  class: normal_state
  style.fill: "#ACE1AF"
  style.stroke: "#2E7D32"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
ILLEGAL_HANDLE: "вќЊ ILLEGAL STATE\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nhandle_client called\nWHILE holding\npool->lock\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nResult: All other\nworkers blocked;\nacquire loop\nstalls; server\ndeadlocks under load\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nNEVER DO THIS" {
  class: error_state
}
exited: "EXITED\n(return NULL)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nThread function\nreturns; pthread_join\nin shutdown completes" {
  shape: rectangle
  style: {
    fill: "#222222"
    font-color: white
    border-radius: 20
    font-size: 13
    stroke: black
    stroke-width: 3
  }
}
initial -> WAITING: "pthread_mutex_lock\n(pool->lock) в–ј\nthen immediately\nenters cond_wait\n(releases lock в–І)" {
  style.stroke: black
  style.stroke-width: 2
}
WAITING -> WOKEN: "cond_signal OR\ncond_broadcast\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\npthread_cond_wait\nreacquires lock в–ј\nautomatically\nbefore returning" {
  style.stroke: "#7B6FD4"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.font-size: 12
}
WOKEN -> WAITING: "while condition TRUE\n(count==0 && !shutdown)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nSpurious wakeup\nor signal consumed\nby another worker\nв†’ re-wait, lock в–ј\nstill held entering\ncond_wait в–І exit" {
  style.stroke: "#7B6FD4"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 4
  style.font-size: 12
}
WOKEN -> SHUTDOWN_CHECK: "while condition FALSE\nbecause shutdown==1\n&& count==0\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nBoth checks done\nunder lock в–ј" {
  style.stroke: "#CC0000"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.font-size: 12
}
WOKEN -> DEQUEUING: "while condition FALSE\nbecause count > 0\n(work available)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nLock в–ј still held\nfrom cond_wait return" {
  style.stroke: "#3A8FB5"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.bold: true
  style.font-size: 12
}
SHUTDOWN_CHECK -> exited: "pthread_mutex_unlock в–І\nreturn NULL\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\npthread_join\nin shutdown\nunblocks" {
  style.stroke: "#444444"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.font-size: 12
}
DEQUEUING -> UNLOCKED: "pthread_mutex_unlock\n(pool->lock) в–І\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nwork_item is\nlocal stack copy;\nno shared state\naccessed after\nthis point without\na separate mutex" {
  style.stroke: "#3A8FB5"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.font-size: 12
}
UNLOCKED -> HANDLING: "Call:\nhandle_client_keep_alive\n(item.client_fd,\n item.client_ip,\n item.client_port,\n g_doc_root)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nlock: NOT HELD в–І\nThis is critical;\nallows true parallelism" {
  style.stroke: "#2E7D32"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.bold: true
  style.font-size: 12
}
HANDLING -> WAITING: "handle_client_keep_alive\nreturns\n(client_fd closed inside)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\npthread_mutex_lock\n(pool->lock) в–ј\nLoop back to top\nGOTO WAITING" {
  style.stroke: "#2E7D32"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.font-size: 12
}
DEQUEUING -> ILLEGAL_HANDLE: "ILLEGAL:\ncalling handle_client\nbefore unlock" {
  style.stroke: "#CC0000"
  style.stroke-width: 3
  style.stroke-dash: 5
  style.font-color: "#CC0000"
  style.bold: true
  style.animated: true
}
legend: {
  near: bottom-right
  label: |md
    **Legend**
    - рџџЈ Purple = Lock HELD в–ј state
    - рџ”µ Blue = Lock transition zone
    - рџџў Green = Lock RELEASED в–І (work happening)
    - вљ« Dark = Terminal / exit
    - рџ”ґ Red = ILLEGAL вЂ” must never occur
    - `в–ј` = pthread_mutex_lock acquired
    - `в–І` = pthread_mutex_unlock released
    - Dashed arrow = spurious/backward transition
    - Animated red = illegal path
  |
  style: {
    fill: "#F5F5F5"
    stroke: "#999999"
    border-radius: 8
    font-size: 12
  }
}
invariants: |md
  **Critical Invariants**
  1. `pool->lock` held at top of loop, in WOKEN, in DEQUEUING вЂ” NEVER in HANDLING
  2. `while` (not `if`) around `pthread_cond_wait` вЂ” mandatory for spurious wakeup safety
  3. `work_item` is value-copied (24 B) before unlock вЂ” no shared pointer after UNLOCKED
  4. `client_fd` closed by `handle_client_keep_alive` before returning to WAITING
  5. `shutdown==1 && count>0` в†’ still DEQUEUES (drains queue before exit)
  6. `pthread_cond_broadcast` used in shutdown (not signal) вЂ” wakes ALL workers
| {
  near: bottom-left
  style: {
    fill: "#FFFDE7"
    stroke: "#F9A825"
    border-radius: 8
    font-size: 12
  }
}